  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Upon reaching 17th level in warlock, increase the dice rolled by your talisman features and invocations to 2d4 and the number of uses is equal to double your proficiency bonus. Additionally, if the wearer of your talisman is a creature other than you, when you would regain a pact magic spell slot through your Eldritch Conduit, you can instead choose to have them regain expended spell slots to recover. The spell slots can have a combined level that is equal to 5th-level. You may use this feature once per long rest.</p><p>For example, they can recover up to 5 levels worth of spell slots. They can recover either a 5th-level spell slot, a 4th-level and 1st-level spell slot, five 1st-level spell slots or other combinations.</p>",
